{"lemma":"تَطاوُلاتٌ","slug":"تَطاوُلاتٌ","root":"ط.#.ل","root_slug":"ط-_-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-_-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"تَطاوُل","root":"طول","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27340"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%B7%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%8F%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lengthen","tags":["intransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"تَطَاوَلَ لَيْلُكَ بِٱلْأَثْمُدِ\n وَنَامَ ٱلْخَلِيُّ وَلَمْ تَرْقُدِ\n وَبَاتَ وَبَاتَتْ لَهُ لَيْلَةٌ\n كَلَيْلَةِ ذِي ٱلْعَائِرِ ٱلْأَرْمَدِ","english":"Long was your night at al-Athmud\n the carefree one slept, but you did not slumber\n he spent the night and it passed for him\n like a night of someone with sore and inflamed eyes"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stretch oneself to see far"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to raise oneself above another, be proud towards"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be powerful"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to overreach"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to take unlawful possession of"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be long or too long"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of تَطَاوَلَ (taṭāwala) (form VI)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare طَوِيل (ṭawīl, “long”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27340","headword_ar":"تطاول","root":"Twl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, former half. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became high by degrees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a building. (L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$yd","text_ar":"شيد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTaAl~a","text_ar":"تَطَالَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTaAlala","text_ar":"تَطَالَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stood upon his toes, and stretched his stature, to look at a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTaAwalotu fiY qiyaAmiY","text_ar":"تَطَاوَلْتُ فِى قِيَامِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I stretched my legs, in my standing, to look."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yataTaAwalu liloA^afonaAni wayajota*ibuhaA biAlmiHojani","text_ar":"يَتَطَاوَلُ لِلْاَفْنَانِ وَيَجْتَذِبُهَا بِالمِحْجَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stretches himself up towards the branches, and draws them to him with the hooked-headed stick"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrq","text_ar":"حرق"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTAwl Ealayohimu","text_ar":"تطاول عَلَيْهِمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ab~u bifaDolihi","text_ar":"الرَّبُّ بِفَضْلِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Lord looked down upon them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded them compassionately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$orafa","text_ar":"اَشْرَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his favour"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made a show of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~uwl","text_ar":"الطُّول"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tallness"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~awol","text_ar":"الطَّوْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTAwl Ealayohi","text_ar":"تطاول عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstTAl","text_ar":"استطال","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same; (Az, S, O, Msb, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He held up his head with a show of superiority over him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he behaved haughtily, arrogantly, overweeningly, overbearingly, domineeringly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proudly, towards him; domineered over him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exalted himself above him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he overbore, overpowered, subdued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oppressed, him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh","text_ar":"عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstTAl","text_ar":"استطال","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he arrogated to himself excellence over him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafaD~ala","text_ar":"تَفَضَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and exalted himself above him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohimo","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstTAlwA","text_ar":"استطالوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they slew of them more than they"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had slain"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of them"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the former]: (O:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY EiroDi Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"فِى عِرْضِ النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAisotiTaAlapu","text_ar":"الاِسْتِطَالَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the contemning of men,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exalting oneself above them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reviling them, vilifying them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detracting from their reputation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tTAwl bimaA Einodahu","text_ar":"تطاول بِمَا عِنْدَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exalted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"magnified,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boasted, himself in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he boasted of, what he possessed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ftH","text_ar":"فتح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaHolu yataTaAwalu EalaY A_ibilihi","text_ar":"الفَحْلُ يَتَطَاوَلُ عَلَى اـِبِلِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stallion"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overbears,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drives as he pleases, and repels the other stallions from, his she-camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTaAwalaA","text_ar":"تَطَاوَلَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They vied, competed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contended for superiority, each with the other"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~uwl","text_ar":"الطُّول"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tallness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~awol","text_ar":"الطَّوْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excel-lence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see 3]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Msb","O"]}]}}